0`\n- GC Reasons: `GRCleanupReasonTTLExpired`, `GRCleanupReasonIdle`, `GRCleanupReasonOrphanCR`, `GRCleanupReasonGhostEntry`\n\n**reconciler/types.go:**\n- Resource types: `resourceTypeAgentRuntime`, `resourceTypeCodeInterpreter`, `resourceTypePod`\n- Results: `resultSuccess`, `resultError`\n- Error types: `errorTypeStoreUnreachable`, `errorTypeListerFailure`, `errorTypeInvalidData`, `errorTypeUpdateFailed`\n- Conditions: `ConditionReady = \"Ready\"`, `ReasonTerminated = \"Terminated\"`\n- Statuses: `StatusPending`, `StatusRunning`, `StatusTerminated`\n- Limits: `maxRetries = 15`, `defaultWorkers = 2`, `cacheSyncTimeout = 30s`, `shutdownTimeout = 30s`\n\n---\n\n### 7. Testing Patterns/Conventions in the Project\n\n**Framework:** Standard `go test` with `github.com/stretchr/testify` (assert, require)\n\n**Common Patterns Observed:**\n1. **Table-driven tests** with `struct{name, input, expected}` and `t.Run()` subtests\n2. **Mock stores** - Simple in-memory map-based implementations (see `mockStore` in sandbox_delete_test.go)\n3. **Gin test context** - `gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)` or `gin.TestMode`, `httptest.NewRecorder()`, `gin.CreateTestContext()`\n4. **Fake K8s clients** - `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)`\n5. **Helper functions** - `newTestMetricsRecorder(t)` with `t.Helper()`\n6. **Nil receiver safety tests** - Testing methods on nil pointers\n7. **Boundary condition tests** - Exact boundary, 1 second before/after\n8. **JSON serialization tests** - Marshal/unmarshal round-trip verification\n9. **Error message assertions** - `assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"expected text\")`\n10. **HTTP response validation** - Status code + JSON body parsing\n\n**Test File Naming:** `<source_file>_test.go` in the same package\n\n---\n\n### 8. Summary of Test Coverage Gaps\n\n| File | Current Coverage | Gap Level |\n|------|-----------------|-----------|\n| `handler/sandbox_create.go` | 0% | CRITICAL - No tests at all |\n| `reconciler/reconciler.go